        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Mon Jul 20 2020 17:07:04 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><ul><li><a href="#markdown介绍">Markdown介绍</a></li><li><a href="#typora简介">Typora简介</a></li><li><a href="#typora常用快捷键"><strong>Typora常用快捷键</strong></a></li><li><a href="#markdown语法">Markdown语法</a><ul><li><a href="#1-目录">1 目录</a></li><li><a href="#2-标题">2 标题</a></li><li><a href="#3-字体">3 字体</a></li><li><a href="#4-引用">4 引用</a></li><li><a href="#5-分割线">5 分割线</a></li><li><a href="#6-插入图片">6 插入图片</a><ul><li><a href="#61-本地图片">6.1 本地图片</a></li><li><a href="#62-网络图片">6.2 网络图片</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#7-列表">7 列表</a><ul><li><a href="#71-无序列表">7.1 无序列表</a></li><li><a href="#72-有序列表">7.2 有序列表</a></li><li><a href="#73-列表嵌套">7.3 列表嵌套</a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><h1><span id="markdown介绍">Markdown介绍</span></h1><p>Markdown 是一种<strong>纯文本格式的标记语言</strong>。</p><h1><span id="typora简介">Typora简介</span></h1><p>Typora是一款<strong>支持即时渲染（实时预览）的Markdown文本编辑器</strong>。</p><h1><span id="typora常用快捷键"><strong>Typora常用快捷键</strong></span></h1><table><thead><tr><th align="center">快捷键</th><th align="center">功能</th><th align="center">快捷键</th><th align="center">功能</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 1</td><td align="center">一级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + B</td><td align="center">字体加粗</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 2</td><td align="center">二级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + I</td><td align="center">字体倾斜</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 3</td><td align="center">三级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + U</td><td align="center">下划线</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 4</td><td align="center">四级标题</td><td align="center">Alt + Shift + 5</td><td align="center">删除线</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 5</td><td align="center">五级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + T</td><td align="center">插入表格</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + 6</td><td align="center">六级标题</td><td align="center">Ctrl + K</td><td align="center">插入链接</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + L</td><td align="center">选中一行</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + I</td><td align="center">插入图片</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + D</td><td align="center">选中一个单词</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + M</td><td align="center">插入公式</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + E</td><td align="center">选中相同格式的文字</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + Q</td><td align="center">插入引用</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + Home</td><td align="center">返回顶部</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + K</td><td align="center">插入代码块</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + End</td><td align="center">返回底部</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Enter</td><td align="center">跳出代码块另起一行</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + F</td><td align="center">查找</td><td align="center">Ctrl + Shift + `</td><td align="center">插入代码片段</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Ctrl + H</td><td align="center">替换</td><td align="center">按相同的快捷键</td><td align="center">取消格式</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li><p>插入链接：Ctrl + K</p><p><a href="www.baidu.com">百度</a></p><p>&lt;<a href="http://www.baidu.com&gt;" target="_blank" rel="noopener">www.baidu.com&gt;</a></p><p><a href>www.baidu.com</a></p></li><li><p>插入代码块：Ctrl + Shift + K</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="JAVA"><figure class="iseeu highlight /java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">printf(<span class="string">"Hello World!"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li><li><p>切换到下一行：Ctrl + Enter</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="JAVA"><figure class="iseeu highlight /java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">printf(<span class="string">"Hello World!"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>光标在这儿（在代码块中跳出代码块另起一行）</p></li><li><p>插入代码片段：Ctrl + Shift + `</p><p><code>printf(&quot;Hello World!&quot;)</code></p></li><li><p>插入图片：Ctrl + Shift + I</p></li></ul><h1><span id="markdown语法">Markdown语法</span></h1><h2><span id="1-目录">1 目录</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="JSON"><figure class="iseeu highlight /json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[toc]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>安装：安装一个<code>hexo-toc</code>的插件，代码如下：</li></ul><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="SQL"><figure class="iseeu highlight /sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> hexo-toc <span class="comment">--save</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>配置：配置站点配置文件<code>_config.yml</code>：</li></ul><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="YAML"><figure class="iseeu highlight /yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">maxdepth:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>使用：在Markdown文章中加入toc的占位符：</li></ul><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="XML"><figure class="iseeu highlight /xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- toc --&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2><span id="2-标题">2 标题</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="CLEAN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 一级标题</span><br><span class="line">## 二级标题</span><br><span class="line">### 三级标题</span><br><span class="line">#### 四级标题</span><br><span class="line">##### 五级标题</span><br><span class="line">###### 六级标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li><p>#与标题内容之间一定要有空格</p></li><li><p>快捷键：一到六阶标题：<code>Ctrl + 1/2/3/4/5/6</code></p><p>​ 普通文本： <code>Ctrl + 0</code></p></li></ul><h2><span id="3-字体">3 字体</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="ASCIIDOC"><figure class="iseeu highlight /asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">*倾斜字体*</span>  </span><br><span class="line">*<span class="strong">*加粗字体*</span>*  </span><br><span class="line">**<span class="strong">*加粗倾斜字*</span>*<span class="strong">*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">&lt;u&gt;这是加下划线的文字&lt;/u&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">~~这是加删除线的文字~~</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li><p>快捷键：<em>倾斜</em>：<code>Ctrl + I</code></p><p>​ <strong>加粗</strong>：<code>Ctrl + B</code></p><p>​ <u>下划线</u>：<code>Ctrl + U</code></p><p>​ <del>删除线</del>：<code>Alt + Shift + 5</code></p></li></ul><h2><span id="4-引用">4 引用</span></h2><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="RUBY"><figure class="iseeu highlight /ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>引用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;</span>&gt;引用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>输入&gt;后面加空格可以连续嵌套</li></ul><blockquote><p>引用</p><blockquote><p>引用</p><blockquote><p>引用</p></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><ul><li>快捷键：<code>Ctrl + Shift + Q</code></li></ul><h2><span id="5-分割线">5 分割线</span></h2><p>三个以上-或*</p><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="YAML"><figure class="iseeu highlight /yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">***</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ul><li>创建.md文件后首行（必须是第一行）输入<code>---</code>，然后按回车可插入<code>Front-matter</code>。</li></ul><h2><span id="6-插入图片">6 插入图片</span></h2><h3><span id="61-本地图片">6.1 本地图片</span></h3><div class="highlight-wrap"autocomplete="off" autocorrect="off" autocapitalize="off" spellcheck="false" contenteditable="true"data-rel="PLAIN"><figure class="iseeu highlight /plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">直接拖进来</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><img src="/1011929149/pig.gif" alt></p><h3><span id="62-网络图片">6.2 网络图片</span></h3><p><img src="https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1595155655173&di=7ef9b7285e79ee09de09d3196ef40f8f&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fres.fsonline.com.cn%2Fa%2F10001%2F201811%2F982345d2a660e22ed247148e81518c0b.gif" alt></p><h2><span id="7-列表">7 列表</span></h2><h3><span id="71-无序列表">7.1 无序列表</span></h3><h3><span id="72-有序列表">7.2 有序列表</span></h3><h3><span id="73-列表嵌套">7.3 列表嵌套</span></h3><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
      
      
